    "type": "message",
    "text": "I love the concept. My worry is about assuring correctness wrt the law, especially in future years. To be quite honest I would want the endorsement of some professionals before using such a thing, and professionals cost a lot (which, yes, makes this a self-sustaining problem. I share your opinion of tax industry lobbyists).",
