  {
    "client_msg_id": "f6d84fb2-6b3b-44e3-b8d3-55f09540a319",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Can you really pull it off in time? The tax code is famously complex, and hasn't had incentives to be simple for at least the life of TurboTax.\n\nDo you have some well-defined subset in mind that you plan to support? That would be one way to deal with the complexity.\n\nI worry that people will lie on their taxes and say that they followed your app when they get audited. That would open you up to legal liability. Particularly if you aren't showing up in their returns as a paid preparer. (Rentierism by licenses.)",
    "user": "UCUSW7WVD",
    "ts": "1612639268.044100",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
